title: JasTrend Vorhees 5/26: Minneapolis Police, Bryce Hall, Jimmy Fallon, SpaceX
itunes:title: JasTrend Vorhees 5/26: Minneapolis Police, Bryce Hall, Jimmy Fallon, SpaceX
description:
On this edition of JasTrend Vorhees Jack and Miles discuss the Minneapolis Police killing George Floyd, an unarmed black man while in custody, two Tik Tok stars were arrested for drug possession, a video has resurfaced of Jimmy doing blackface in the early 2000's, and SpaceX is going to launch its first manned-mission.
